    {
      "id": "moe-jacc-txt", "type": "text",
      "x": 475, "y": 266, "width": 380, "height": 80,
      "text": "bias_affinity_jaccard ★ 核心指标\n|A ∩ B| / |A ∪ B|\nA = bias前路由  B = bias后路由\n⚠ 低值 → Router 偏好被 Bias 强行扭转",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#343a40", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
