    {
      "id": "moe-enorm-txt", "type": "text",
      "x": 58, "y": 484, "width": 380, "height": 80,
      "text": "expert_norm — 专家发展均衡度\n||concat(w1, w2)||₂ 逐专家计算\n输出 mean / std / min / max\n⚠ min极小→萎缩  max极大→过载  std高→不均衡",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
