      "x": 475, "y": 484, "width": 380, "height": 80,
      "text": "shared_expert / shared_routed_ratio\nshared_norm = ||shared_params||₂\nratio = shared_norm / mean(routed_norms)\n⚠ <0.3 共享无效  >3.0 MoE 退化为 Dense",
